One we hear a lot nowadays: “When is the Mueller report coming — and what will it say?”Our answer: We don’t know.
We don’t know what Mueller will report, when he will report it or even whether we’ll be able to read it.
When Mueller is done, he has to give a report to Attorney General William Barr.
And, of course, there are lots of areas worthy of scrutiny beyond Russia: Trump’s businesses, his inauguration, his hush money payments and more.
